item.title: St Mary’s put to the sword
item.author: Arvind Rajagopalan,Yash Verma,
item.description: In a near-repeat performance of his previous match as captain, stand-in skipper Vignesh Venkateshwaran led a squad with a depletedbatting line up to a 58-run victory over a much-vaunted St. Mary’s side who had recorded some big wins of their own leading up to this match. Imperial was put in to bat …
